According to this plan , it was decided that <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Britain</ENAMEX> would use a dam in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Uganda</ENAMEX> in order to lower the water level in <ENAMEX TYPE="LOC">the White Nile</ENAMEX> by seven - eighths .
